title: PC Today 3 ed. Apr-June 2014
description:
PC Today is a monthly mobile computing and technology magazine published by Sandhills Publishing Company in Lincoln, Nebraska, USA

The article and editorial content focuses primarily around mobile and wireless technologies, notebooks, mobile phones, PDAs, Windows, and office and home software[1]. PC Today is distributed to business-class hotels, airline clubs, and FBOs. The magazine also includes classified advertising
